result.name: 周昌隆餐廳厨坊

reviews.text: Looks like a local coffee restaurant selling both western snacks, pasta and chinese dishes. Price is fair, food quality is acceptable.
芙蓉蛋飯 is my favourite dish here
good

很久以前有來過這間位於街市的茶餐廳吃過晚飯。
雖然之後隔了好久好久也沒有再來過了，
這天突然早上想吃沙嗲牛肉麵就想起這裡了！
說來還是第一次在這吃早餐，沒想到選擇也是頗多的

我點的是 - 懷舊港式早餐B ($33)
在四款中可揀兩款配～選了雞蛋和腸仔。
蛋或者選炒蛋會比較好？現在這個煎蛋的貌相實的不太討好。
還有牛油方包，烘了底要+$1 ~ 那牛油實在太少了吧！！

沙嗲牛肉麵 - 比起很久之前來吃常餐的“沙嗲牛肉”更為濃味！
牛肉也多了不少且很嫩，麵條亦仍然保持彈牙。
不知道是不是隔了一段時間，這裡換了廚師，還是廚師進步了呢?
這個餐廳不錯、價廉物美、服務又好、環境舒服...不防來試一試...😘😘😘

reviews.text: Lots of fresh seafood, poultry and vegetables. There are cooked food stalls as well. Beef noodles are very delicious and good value.
Clean, modern wet market - friendly stallholders. As a non-Cantonese speaker you'll be fine with pointing at what you want and a few mm gois. The prices are very reasonable!
Clean n neat wet market
nice market, price is cheap than nearby supermarket,

Well! This market is a combination of supermarket and traditional wet market. Traditional wet market may give you a depression of disorder, stinky, smelly. But fortunately, from the day that Link the company reopen the market everything change. It's a good place for tourist!
